Metadata: State of the Bay Research Symposium 2015 (Bellingham Bay)
State of the Bay Research Symposium, Bellingham, Washington, January 22, 2015
University of Washington, Sea Grant College Program

On January 22, 2015 researchers, managers, and community members came together at the State of the Bay Research Symposium. The purpose of the Symposium was to share the latest science, explore management challenges, and enhance collaborations and partnerships in our efforts to protect Bellingham Bay. For the individual PowerPoint presentations, go to: http://wha​tcom.wsu.edu/nr​/sotb/
